snippet: Police and spy agencies are close to identifying the English-accented militant depicted on video showing the killing of U.S. journalist James Foley, Britain's ambassador to the United States said Sunday....

headline.print_headline: Ambassador: UK Close to Identifying Foley Killer
headline.main: Ambassador: UK Close to Identifying Foley Killer

lead_paragraph: Police and spy agencies are close to identifying the English-accented militant depicted on video showing the killing of U.S. journalist James Foley, Britain's ambassador to the United States said Sunday.
